INSERT INTO ask_answer VALUES ('1957','9706','我想在首页按ID调用前十五位的会员列表，请名如何调用','sdf_sky','26','1357716781','1357752414','<p>现在把实现方式填写下来：</p><p>1、修改tipask/model/user.class.php文件，加入新的方法：</p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false;\">function get_top15($start=0, $limit=15){\r\n    $userlist = array();\r\n    $query = $this-&gt;db-&gt;query(\"select * from \" . DB_TABLEPRE . \"user  order by uid ASC limit $start,$limit\");\r\n    while ($user = $this-&gt;db-&gt;fetch_array($query)) {\r\n        $user[\'lastlogintime\'] = tdate($user[\'lastlogin\']);\r\n        $user[\'regtime\'] = tdate($user[\'regtime\']);\r\n        $userlist[] = $user;\r\n    }\r\n    return $userlist;\r\n}</pre><p>2、在页面中调用该方法并输出用户信息（例如在tipask/view/default/index.html中调用）</p><pre class=\"brush:html;toolbar:false;\">&lt;ul&gt;    &lt;!--{eval $this-&gt;load(\"user\");}--&gt;\r\n    &lt;!--{eval $userlist=$_ENV[\'user\']-&gt;get_top15();}--&gt;\r\n    &lt;!--{loop $userlist $user}--&gt;\r\n    &lt;!--{eval ++$index;}--&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        &lt;span class=\"hyname\"&gt;&lt;img align=\"absmiddle\" src=\"{SITE_URL}css/default/num{$index}.gif\"&gt; &lt;a target=\"_blank\" href=\"{url user/space/$user[\'uid\']}\"&gt;{$user[\'username\']}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n        &lt;img align=\"absmiddle\" src=\"{SITE_URL}css/default/up.gif\"&gt;{$user[\'credit1\']}\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;!--{/loop}--&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;</pre><p>好了，这样就可以了。<br /></p>','谢谢您的解答！','1','114.247.88.27','','1','0');
